<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Homepage</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Our Application</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="homepage-container">
        <div class="intro-text">
            <h2>Welcome to Our Platform</h2>
            <p>Our application provides a comprehensive suite of tools to help you manage your tasks and stay organized. Whether you're here to sign up for a new account or to sign in to an existing one, you're in the right place!</p>
            <p><strong>Sign Up:</strong> Create a new account to access all the features our application has to offer. Registration is quick and easy, and you'll be set up in no time.</p>
            <p><strong>Sign In:</strong> If you already have an account, simply sign in to start using our platform. Enter your email and password to access your personalized dashboard and continue where you left off.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-container">
            <div class="auth-form">
                <h2>Sign Up</h2>
                <p>Register to access all features of our application. Start by creating your account today!</p>
                <a href="/signup">
                    <button>Sign Up</button>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="auth-form">
                <h2>Sign In</h2>
                <p>Already have an account? Log in to your existing account and resume your activities.</p>
                <a href="/signin">
                    <button>Sign In</button>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
